		<title>几种热门瘦身果蔬汁品牌（几种热门瘦身果蔬汁）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/9477.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 05:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[圣女]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[牛油果]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[食材]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=9477</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[双莓汁 食材：草莓10颗、蓝莓1小把 草莓和蓝莓都是gi值很低的水果（糖分越低，gi值越低），保护心血管防癌都 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">双莓汁</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/eec975ef37530041981e3cd81b732d26.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：草莓10颗、蓝莓1小把</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">草莓和蓝莓都是gi值很低的水果（糖分越低，gi值越低），保护心血管防癌都有一套，关键是好吃~蓝莓的酸加上草莓的甜，刚好打出酸酸甜甜的双莓汁，超好喝！</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蜜桃圣女果汁</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8222d701f14c215a1bcea499b411d9c2.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：蜜桃2个、圣女果10个</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">粉嫩水灵的蜜桃，搭上酸甜的圣女果，非常清新好喝。蜜桃没有上市时，也可以用李子或西梅代替</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">牛油果养乐多</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/9a92246d61dacc4f8a91d335c5c6f9e0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：养乐多2瓶、牛油果1个</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">牛油果营养又抗氧化，可是单吃真的不好吃呀！加上冰凉酸爽的养乐多，好喝到没朋友~</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">燕麦慕斯</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/e1136035a351e82886e8898f44b16757.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：牛油果1个、猕猴桃1个、燕麦1把、牛奶250ml</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">慕斯通常都很醇厚，基本吃完一杯就饱了，用来做代餐特别好。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">生菜圣女果汁</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/d4a2b5f25549c3847483bafd6941b7a6.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：生菜1小颗、圣女果10个</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">要是嫌味道淡，也可以加半根香蕉进去，会更顺口~</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">排毒清痘汁</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5f242565ea021a23d49cc9c475bfe12e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：纯牛奶1盒、胡萝卜半个、苹果半个、梨半个、蜂蜜2勺、卷心菜2片、山药1小节</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">最后附送一个祛痘小秘方，刚开始可能会有轻微腹泻，因为在排除身体里的毒素之类，慢慢就会好了。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">菠菜香蕉奇异果</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/29b52ed6de2a82f4a294e22a5b8b0de9.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">食材：奇异果1个、香蕉1个、菠菜1小把</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">菠菜维生素丰富，但生吃味道比较难以下咽。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">打成蔬果汁就不怕了，猕猴桃和香蕉的味道把菠菜味盖过，非常适合用来做代餐。</p>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
